import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Alert,
  Button,
} from '@mui/material';
import { Download, Assessment } from '@mui/icons-material';

const Reports = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
        Reports & Transparency
      </Typography>

      <Alert severity="info" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
        Comprehensive reporting and transparency for all blue carbon MRV activities
      </Alert>

      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Project Reports
              </Typography>
              <Typography color="textSecondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                Individual project progress and carbon credit generation
              </Typography>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                startIcon={<Assessment />}
                fullWidth
              >
                Generate Project Report
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                System Overview
              </Typography>
              <Typography color="textSecondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                Overall system performance and impact metrics
              </Typography>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                startIcon={<Assessment />}
                fullWidth
              >
                View System Dashboard
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Blockchain Transactions
              </Typography>
              <Typography color="textSecondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                All blockchain transactions for transparency
              </Typography>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                startIcon={<Assessment />}
                fullWidth
              >
                View Blockchain History
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Export Data
              </Typography>
              <Typography color="textSecondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                Download reports in various formats
              </Typography>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                startIcon={<Download />}
                fullWidth
              >
                Export Reports
              </Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Environmental Impact Summary
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={2} sx={{ mt: 1 }}>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                  <Box textAlign="center">
                    <Typography variant="h4" color="primary">127</Typography>
                    <Typography color="textSecondary">Hectares Restored</Typography>
                  </Box>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                  <Box textAlign="center">
                    <Typography variant="h4" color="secondary">2,340</Typography>
                    <Typography color="textSecondary">Carbon Credits</Typography>
                  </Box>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                  <Box textAlign="center">
                    <Typography variant="h4" color="success.main">15</Typography>
                    <Typography color="textSecondary">Communities</Typography>
                  </Box>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                  <Box textAlign="center">
                    <Typography variant="h4" color="warning.main">95%</Typography>
                    <Typography color="textSecondary">Verification Rate</Typography>
                  </Box>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Reports;
